lyrics:
In a world full of stars, there's my Mikki shining bright,
From that party at Hailey's, our love took flight.
First laid eyes on you, my heart skipped a beat,
In your smile, my future, so sweet.

Oh Mikki, my Babygirl, my guiding light,
With you by my side, everything's just right.
From our first date at the family reunion,
To the laughter we share, it's all pure communion.

Hand in hand, it felt so right,
Like destiny's plan, in the glow of the night.
Your laughter, your grace, like a soothing song,
In your arms, I know I belong.

Oh Mikki, my Babygirl, my guiding light,
With you by my side, everything's just right.
From our first date at the family reunion,
To the laughter we share, it's all pure communion.
